{"body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"optionalauthenticate\">\n<span id=\"id1\"></span><h1>optionalAuthenticate</h1>\n<p>Authenticates a request by checking credentials supplied in the request and extracts a value\nrepresenting the authenticated principal, or <cite>None</cite> if no credentials were supplied.</p>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"signature\">\n<h2>Signature</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight-scala\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span class=\"k\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">optionalAuthenticate</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">T</span><span class=\"o\">](</span><span class=\"n\">auth</span><span class=\"k\">:</span> <span class=\"k\">\u21d2</span> <span class=\"kt\">Future</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">Authentication</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">T</span><span class=\"o\">]])(</span><span class=\"k\">implicit</span> <span class=\"n\">executor</span><span class=\"k\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">ExecutionContext</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"k\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Directive1</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">Option</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">T</span><span class=\"o\">]]</span>\n<span class=\"k\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">optionalAuthenticate</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">T</span><span class=\"o\">](</span><span class=\"n\">auth</span><span class=\"k\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">ContextAuthenticator</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">T</span><span class=\"o\">])(</span><span class=\"k\">implicit</span> <span class=\"n\">executor</span><span class=\"k\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">ExecutionContext</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"k\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Directive1</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">Option</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">T</span><span class=\"o\">]]</span>\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n<p>The signature shown is simplified, the real signature uses magnets. <a class=\"footnote-reference\" href=\"#id3\" id=\"id2\">[1]</a></p>\n<table class=\"docutils footnote\" frame=\"void\" id=\"id3\" rules=\"none\">\n<colgroup><col class=\"label\" /><col /></colgroup>\n<tbody valign=\"top\">\n<tr><td class=\"label\"><a class=\"fn-backref\" href=\"#id2\">[1]</a></td><td>See <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/blog/2012-12-13-the-magnet-pattern/\">The Magnet Pattern</a> for an explanation of magnet-based overloading.</td></tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"description\">\n<h2>Description</h2>\n<p>The <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">optionalAuthenticate</span></tt> directive is similar to the <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">authenticate</span></tt> directive but always extracts an <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">Option</span></tt>\nvalue instead of rejecting the request if no credentials could be found.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n", "display_toc": true, "title": "optionalAuthenticate", "sourcename": "", "customsidebar": null, "current_page_name": "documentation/spray-routing/security-directives/optionalAuthenticate", "next": {"link": "../../examples/", "title": "Complete Examples"}, "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["documentation/spray-routing/examples", "Complete Examples", "N", "next"], ["documentation/spray-routing/security-directives/authorize", "authorize", "P", "previous"]], "meta": {}, "parents": [{"link": "../../../", "title": "Documentation"}, {"link": "../../", "title": "spray-routing"}, {"link": "../../predefined-directives-by-trait/", "title": "Predefined Directives (by trait)"}, {"link": "../", "title": "SecurityDirectives"}], "sidebars": null, "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">optionalAuthenticate</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#signature\">Signature</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#description\">Description</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n", "prev": {"link": "../authorize/", "title": "authorize"}, "metatags": ""}